                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17860719-19-off88 t17860719-19-cd89"></join> last, three gallons of varnish, value 18 s. eight pounds weight of 
                     <persName id="t17860719-19-person262">
                        terra
                         de Seina
